{"tid":1373972,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（發夢攻略）齊裝真係會救你一命，入黎聽故","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:47:05.000Z","uid":25846,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b5634276e9891d8edfe6862a3ed3e3abccdd3e34","tid":1373972,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"岩岩發完夢黎，夢入面我地係元朗西鐵b出口<br />\n當時南邊圍班手足鼓燥起黎<br />\n話有防最狗<br />\n手足就開始氣勢洶洶，敲野出聲。<br />\n見當時實質未有咩行動<br />\n班狗已經開始驚<br />\n放催淚彈，第一時間中嘅係無辜嘅記者已經好慘<br />\n之後b出口有人鬧黑警，繼而向黑警掉石頭<br />\n下一瞬間黑警就開槍<br />\n射向A pt 下面有圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XWLR8eA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXWLR8eA.png&h=d5d40284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA pt姐係上西鐵站條樓梯<br />\n個到原本係撤走嘅主要路線<br />\n當時黑警不停對住個到開槍<br />\n根本係唔撚比人走<br />\n<br />\n最憤怒嘅係我當時係b pt <br />\n同a pt根本係兩個射撃目標<br />\n而且b pt 兄弟當時係冇任何動作，只係待機<br />\n忽然我見到格黎有位兄弟頭上嘅頭盔有野爆開，大聲一啪<br />\n我身上仲即時佔有左d彈爆開後嘅碎屑<br />\n我即刻好撚驚，點解我地冇做任何野<br />\n都可以比人射！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重點黎<br />\n如果個位兄弟冇帶頭盔<br />\n佢好可能已經頭部中槍出血<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n記撚得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">出黎要齊裝<br />\n出黎要齊裝<br />\n出黎要齊裝</span><br />\n<br />\n同場加影 :<br />\n有一下黑警係元朗馬路十字口對上橋位大叫<br />\n屌你老母射夠未<br />\n當時佢比手足嘅激光射左好耐<br />\n事實反映真係有效<br />\n遠攻一流<br />\n你知啦咁夜梗要搵d野照明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抖抖先"},{"pid":"08c626414dc149e3e70901937c35813f1c8fac74","tid":1373972,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e98bed7eae8542f6b325ea863f7ea60bb5386c8","tid":1373972,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:51:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c55d5aa999e88cb1eda9badb45942840bc6548b","tid":1373972,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69c677af87ba0748b9573cd261e54348ec4e7134","tid":1373972,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:52:01.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講 我有權唔解鎖 我要搵律師 我唔簽任何文件 我唔信任何警察 我要警誡記錄 我要食飯 飲水 毛氈 去廁所 我唔舒服要去醫院 我要睇你委任證同編號投訴你</code></pre>"},{"pid":"33f412ece7c62bdc9979134fe2dda885dd645035","tid":1373972,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:55:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"998d3e2fb880635b5d02b001bf3931b4fadea837","tid":1373972,"uid":269285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:28:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b354ab6b3c98428f10b9348cb6fef0a2d44cd111","tid":1373972,"uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:32:08.000Z","msg":"手足唔想咁易就醫院見<br />\n就要齊裝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再成日dum低裝備咁大嘥"},{"pid":"727135a658d2fdb498b659a4aa6d3af60c5daee5","tid":1373972,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:30:34.000Z","msg":"推呀咁重要都冇人睇！"},{"pid":"9c500efe862f6f60b4caa5a8c68ac15057360ad6","tid":1373972,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"睇Live 見有個人發夢果陣, 個木盾下方俾(可能)橡膠子彈射爆左....<br />\n然後個盾頂到個肚....應該無咩事..."},{"pid":"3508fbb87dc9266115fa1ed63cbf2809a0005faf","tid":1373972,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"push"}]}